description:
A set of rare items that revives and heals your entire party and restores their BP.

Spirit Incense x 5
Brave Seed x 5

*These items can also be obtained in-game.
*These items can be claimed from the DLC tab on the Item page.
*If maximum capacity is exceeded, the excess is discarded.
name: Trails of Cold Steel III: Spirit Incense Set 3
